Links to Guilded, YouTube, Facebook, Discord, Twitter, and Twitch must be wrapped in the applicable Policy API or listed in the Social Networks and Social Links settings of your profile or experience description page. english: Roblox does not permit attempts to threaten users in order to force them to do something they do not want to do.
